<div class="com-share" data-id="11254" data-title="《来上海，看看法国人脑洞大开的食物设计展》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/11254/medium/11254.jpg?1436641319" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/11254.html?from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=1" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
